@startuml
actor User
participant LoginController
participant AuthService
participant SpringBackend
participant SceneManager

User -> LoginController : 点击登录按钮
LoginController -> AuthService : login(username, password)
AuthService -> SpringBackend : POST /auth/login
SpringBackend --> AuthService : 返回 token, userInfo
AuthService --> LoginController : 返回 AuthResult

LoginController -> SpringBackend : GET /user/profile
SpringBackend --> LoginController : 返回 userData

LoginController -> SceneManager : switchView("Main")
SceneManager -> User : 显示主界面
@enduml
